        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>No China in Index Funds Act</strong></p><p>This bill prohibits index funds from investing in Chinese companies. Index funds with investments in Chinese companies on the date of enactment have 180 days to divest. The bill establishes civil penalties for violations.&nbsp;</p>]]></text>
